headline: PRTA Dives 53.5% YTD: Will the Restructuring Effort Boost Prospects?
summary: Prothena slashes 63% of its workforce and axes birtamimab after trial failure, reshaping its pipeline and financial outlook. Shares plunge 53.5% YTD.
